ygData.msgSnippet: Doesn t take that long to use up a stack of foraged grubs, I always forage and save the grubs...when I get a stack of 20 I spend a few minutes before logging
ygData.messageBody:
Doesn't take that long to use up a stack of foraged grubs, I always forage
and save the grubs...when I get a stack of 20 I spend a few minutes before
logging using them up. I have fished so much that I have broken a total of
4 fishing rods since April 1999.

Free bait = Fishing Skill 128

Free fish contributed to:

Brewing Skill 124 and Baking Skill 84

-Faras

(Didn't I say I was a stat freak?)

>
> And if you spent the same time killing mobs you'd probably
> come out with
> more cash and more exp for the same time spent. Fishing at
> low levels is
> only worth the time spent on it if you put an extremely low value on
> your time.
